onsibility to read the assigned papers and cases as well as be prepared to discuss them in class. The success of this course will depend heavily on your preparation, participation and willingness to ask probing questions about the broader topic instead of just the specifics of any one paper or case."}, "outline": {"ch": "Preliminaries, Capital Budgeting, Risk and Return, Capital Structure, M＆As, Payout Policy, ESG", "en": "Preliminaries, Capital Budgeting, Risk and Return, Capital Structure, M＆As, Payout Policy, ESG"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Required Materials: Lecture notes, Journal articles and Harvard Business School cases, Corporate Finance (13th ed.), by Ross, Westerfield, and Jaffe, McGraw-Hill, 2022", "en": "Required Materials: Lecture notes, Journal articles and Harvard Business School cases, Corporate Finance (13th ed.), by Ross, Westerfield, and Jaffe, McGraw-Hill, 2022"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "60%", "en": "60%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "Presentation and Written Report55％\nParticipation and bonus marks20％\n2 exams25％ (mid-term exam: 10％, Final Exam: 15％)", "en": "Presentation and Written Report55％\nParticipation and bonus marks20％\n2 exams25％ (mid-term exam: 10％, Final Exam: 15％)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "Wednesday 16:00-17:00 (or by appointment)", "en": "Wednesday 16:00-17:00 (or by appointment)"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "自主學習", "en": "You may utilize the time for self-study, no class meetings."}, "domain": {"ch": "財務金融", "en": "財務金融"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "社會責任", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"